Deadpool 2 final trailer is giving us the chills. The story goes: After surviving a near fatal bovine attack, a disfigured cafeteria chef (played by Wade Wilson) struggles to fulfill his dream of becoming Mayberry’s hottest bartender while also learning to cope with his lost sense of taste. Searching to regain his spice for life, as well as a flux capacitor, Wade must battle ninjas, the yakuza, and a pack of sexually aggressive canines, as he journeys around the world to discover the importance of family, friendship, and flavor – finding a new taste for adventure and earning the coveted coffee mug title of World’s Best Lover.  The film will  be out May 18. Read More: Deadpool Auctions Suit To Fight Cancer